flow effectively.</p></div><div id="styling" class="template-details"><h2 class="title">Styling</h2><p class="paragraph instructions">Below you can find some general rules regarding styling your template.</p><h2 class="title instructions">Color</h2><p class="paragraph instructions">Below you can find some general rules regarding styling your template.</p><div class="spacer-medium"></div><p class="paragraph instructions">To change color swatches:</p><p class="paragraph instructions">1. Click on the element with the color you want to edit.<br>2. In the styles tab on the right, find the color option (ex. Text color)<br>3. Click on the color square.<br>4. Once the little pop-up opens, click the edit icon and choose a new color.<br>5. Click save.</p><div class="spacer-medium"></div><h2 class="title instructions">Fonts</h2><p class="paragraph instructions">The fonts can be downloaded at Google Fonts. These fonts are 100% free for personal and commercial use.</p><div class="spacer-small"></div><p class="paragraph instructions">You can change fonts globally by:<br>1. Selecting "Body" <br>2. In the styles tab on the right, click selector and select "Body (All pages)<br>3. "Scroll down to "Typography" and change for the desired font.</p></div><div id="editing" class="template-details display-none" style=""><h2 class="title">Editing</h2><p class="paragraph instructions">All graphical assets in this template are licensed for personal and commercial use. If you'd like to use a specific asset, please check the license below.</p></div><div id="support" class="template-details"><h2 class="title">Support</h2><p class="paragraph instructions">Animal Cove provides a strong foundation, but we understand your organization might have unique needs. Our customization options allow you to tailor the template perfectly to your vision. <br><br>Let's discuss how we can create a website that flawlessly reflects your brand and mission.<br><br>I can also assist you with:<br>‍<br>1. Template Installation: I can help you install and set up the Animal Cove template on your Webflow account.<br>2. Customization: I can customize the template to match your specific needs and branding.<br>3. Consultation: I can provide you with a consultation to discuss your website requirements and how Animal Cove can be used to achieve your goals.<br><br>Don't hesitate to contact me with any questions about the template or its features.<br><br>Together, we can create a website that helps you connect more pets with loving homes. Contact me today to get started!<br><br>Please note that customization services are not included in the template price. Contact me for a quote.</p></div></div></div></div></section><a href="#page-wrapper" data-w-id="8f827f89-6747-95e9-411d-0e906dcaed6e" class="to-top-button w-inline-block w--current" style="transform: translate3d(0px, 54%, 0px) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0deg, 0deg); transform-style: preserve-3d; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); will-change: transform;"><div class="to-top-button-icon w-icon-slider-left" style="color: rgb(142, 204, 20);"></div></a></div> <?php include('structure/_footer.php'); ?></div><script src="https://d3e54v103j8qbb.cloudfront.net/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.dc5e7f18c8.js?site=65c75049e171bdd6b12f3e86" type="text/javascript" integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script><script src="assets/js/binx.d35332b56.js" type="text/javascript"></script></body></html>